12
13 NEW SECTION. Section 7. Transfer of funds. By July 1, 2025, the state treasurer shall transfer $5
14 million from the general fund capital developments long-range building program account established in 17-7-
15 209 to the firefighting training facility infrastructure account established in [section 2].
16
17 NEW SECTION. Section 8. Appropriation. There is appropriated $5 million from the firefighting
18 training facility infrastructure account established in [section 2] to the department of military affairs for the
19 biennium beginning July 1, 2025, for grants authorized in [sections 3 through 5]. Appropriations are authorized
20 to continue through the biennium beginning July 1, 2029.
21
22 NEW SECTION. Section 9. Effective date. [This act] is effective July 1, 2025.
23
24 NEW SECTION. Section 10. Termination. [This act] terminates June 30, 2031.
